headline: Lennar To Acquire Rausch Coleman Homes
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B) announced today that it has entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Rausch Coleman Homes, a residential homebuilder based in Fayetteville, Arkansas. Lennar will acquire Rausch Coleman's homebuilding operations, which expects to deliver approximately 5,000 homes with an average sales price of $230,000 in calendar year 2024.
